OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 01 MAY
OL,4,CTV TRANSMITTERS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1953FThe BBC TV Glencairn 405-line
OL,7,FVHF transmitter is brought into
OL,8,Fservice. This is the first TV
OL,9,Ftransmitter in Northern Ireland.
OL,10,
OL,11,FThis temporary mobile transmitter was
OL,12,Fone of a number set up in the UK in
OL,13,F1953 to provide coverage of the
OL,14,FCoronation broadcast, in advance of
OL,15,Fpermanent transmitters being built.
OL,16,
OL,17,FWork on a larger, more powerful,
OL,18,Fpermanent transmitter located on Divis
OL,19,Fmountain was already underway.
